description:
Choo choo! In this challenge, I build on chapter 3 (Oscillating Motion) of the Nature of Code series and simulate a simple pendulum in p5.js via angular acceleration. https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/159-simple-pendulum-simulation.html

🕹️ p5.js Simple Pendulum https://editor.p5js.org/codingtrain/sketches/SN-39sHAC
🕹️ p5.js OOP Pendulum: https://editor.p5js.org/codingtrain/sketches/lJz1cmMp4
🕹️ p5.js Pendulum Array: https://editor.p5js.org/codingtrain/sketches/Bj82tUlIO
🎥 Pendulum Array Exploration: https://youtu.be/dpqNqyQCcbY?t=2283

🎥 Previous Coding Challenge: https://youtu.be/3MqJzMvHE3E?list=PLRqwX-V7Uu6ZiZxtDDRCi6uhfTH4FilpH
